NK036(chi)027:1: // grub thob me long rdo rje'i rnam thar dri log ma bzhugs so //
NK036(chi)027:3: chos sku'i bla ma dmigs med ngang //
NK036(chi)027:4: longs sku'i bla ma 'od gsal sku //
NK036(chi)027:5: sprul sku'i bla ma thugs rje can //
NK036(chi)027:6: bla ma gsum la gsol ba 'debs //
NK036(chi)027:7: dug gsum grol bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK036(chi)027:8: chos dbyings bla ma mi rtog dang //
NK036(chi)027:9: me longs bla ma gsal dag lha //
NK036(chi)027:10: mnyam nyid bla ma mtho dma' med //
NK036(chi)027:11: sor rtog bla ma ma 'dres gsal //
NK036(chi)027:12: bya grub bla ma rigs 'khor bcas //
NK036(chi)027:13: bla ma lnga la gsol ba 'debs //
NK036(chi)027:14: dug lnga grol bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK036(chi)027:16: byin rlabs rtogs pas 'khor mdzad bla ma dang //
NK036(chi)027:17: bsgrubs pas dngos grub 'byung ba yi dam lha //
NK036(chi)027:18: 'ur bas gzhan snang thul ba mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK036(chi)027:19: byin gyis rlobs shig rjes 'jug thugs rjes zungs //
NK036(chi)027:20: mos pas thugs dgongs gcig gyur chos mdzad dang //
NK036(chi)027:21: rtogs pas dgongs don grol ba dam pa'i chos //
NK036(chi)027:22: dam tshig gtsang bas bsgrubs pa'i chos skyong rnams //
NK036(chi)027:23: bstan pa srungs shig bar chad rkyen rnams sol //
NK036(chi)027:26: sgrags nang rtug pa me long la //
NK036(chi)027:27: 'phreng po'i ston pa dbang phyug khong //
NK036(chi)027:28: dri log rnam thar zhu'o zer //
NK036(chi)027:29: shog bur 'chal gtam kha gcig longs //
NK036(chi)027:31: de ltar nyon mongs la dmigs su med pa chos sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:32: rang rgyud rtsub la stong pa chos sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:33: 'du shes 'dus la mtha' dang bral ba chos sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:34: de gsum chos sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:36: mtha' bral gcig tu bsdus pa longs sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:37: gcig gi ye shes lnga stong pa mdangs dang ldan pa longs sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:38: cang med zhi khro sku ru gsal ba longs sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:39: de gsum longs sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:41: ma byin par gzhan gyi chung ma la rku ba sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:42: mi tshangs pa rang gi bu mo la spyod pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:43: rdzun bla ma la gtong ba sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:44: srog gcod rang gi bu phrug gsod pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:45: 'grogs gzhung yon bdag dang rtsod pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:46: mje a ma la ston pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:47: mi ngas chung ma la byed pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:48: rang re'i bla ma rang res chog pa sprul sku me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:49: de rnams sprul sku me long gi rnam thar bsdus pa'o //
NK036(chi)027:51: bla ma rnams dang rmi lam du mjal ba rdzun rkyal me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:52: bstan gtso dang thugs rje chen po dang phag mo
NK036(chi)027:53: dang lhan skyes dang rta mgrin rnams kyi zhal mthong
NK036(chi)027:54: ba rdzun rkyal me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:55: rdzogs pa chen po snying tig zab pa'i yon tan
NK036(chi)027:56: gyis bdag dang 'brel tshad don dang ldan pa rdzun
NK036(chi)027:57: rkyal me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:58: de gsum rdzun rkyal me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:60: rdo la rdog rjes bdun brgyad byung ba zog po me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:61: brag rgod mche ba la g.yung drung ris dang lag
NK036(chi)027:62: rjes rgyab pa zog po me long gi rnam thar
NK036(chi)027:63: / rmang spus rgyal bsen thub pa zog po me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:64: de gsum zog po me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:66: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs dran pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:67: rtag tu 'chi ba dran pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:68: bla ma mtshan ldan 'tshol ba chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:69: mos gus gsol ba 'debs pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:70: rgyu 'bras la thub tshad 'dzem pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:71: dag snang btub tshad kyis sbyangs pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:72: bla ma phyogs med la mos gus byed pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:73: gdams ngag zab mo zhu ba chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:74: de tsho la 'brel pa dum re 'jog pa chos pa me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:75: de rnams chos pa me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:77: zhen log dgos med du 'byongs pa ri khrod me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:78: dben gnas brag phug 'dzin pa ri khrod me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:79: 'phong la tsher ma zugs pa bzhin byed pa ri khrod me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:80: de gsum ri khrod me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:82: dka' thub sna tshogs byed pa ltogs brka ma me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:83: ras rkyang gyon zhing khyi lpags 'ding ba ltogs brkam me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:84: bla ma rnams la gdams ngag zhu ba'i phyag rten
NK036(chi)027:85: dang tshogs 'khor du ba la byed pa ltogs brkam
NK036(chi)027:87: de gsum ltogs brkam me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:89: rgya nad dang shig nad zhugs pa dbang chung me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:90: slong mos bzhad gad du gyur pa dbang chung me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:91: rngan chen rgyun chad med pa dbang chung me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:92: de gsum dbang chung me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:94: bla ma rnams kyi thugs rjes bzung ba grub thob me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:95: mi 'gyur phag mos bcug pa grub thob me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:96: dus ngan gyi snang ba bde shos su 'dug pa grub thob me log gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:97: de gsum grub thob me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:99: ngo bo stong nyid du rtogs pa rtogs ldan me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:100: rang bzhin ye shes lnga ldan du rtogs pa rtogs ldan me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:101: thugs rjes sku gsum kun khyab tu rtogs pa rtogs ldan me long gi rnam thar /
NK036(chi)027:102: de gsum rtogs ldan me long gi rnam thar ro //
NK036(chi)027:104: chos sku me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:105: rang gi ngo bo rtogs par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:106: longs sku me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:107: rang gi rang bzhin rtogs par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:108: sprul sku me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:109: mtshang ngan phyi ru phyin par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:110: rdzun rkyal me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:111: nga rgyal dbyings su dag par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:112: zog po me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:113: chags sdang rang sar dag par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:114: chos pa me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:115: mi tshe bzang la skyel bar mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:116: ri khrod me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:117: zhen chags gting nas med par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:118: ltogs brkam me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:119: chos phyogs sdug bsran thub par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:120: grub thob me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:121: gang yin mgo ni thon par mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:122: rtogs ldan me long gi rnam thar gyis //
NK036(chi)027:125: sprang po me long rdo rje yi //
NK036(chi)027:126: rnam thar bcu gcig brtsam yig ma //
NK036(chi)027:127: ston pa dbang phyug thugs dgyes mdzod //
NK036(chi)027:128: sgrags nang rtug pa me long gi rnam thar dri log ma zhes bya ba rdzogs so //
